Mods.Name: ScriptHookV
Mods.Title: Script Hook V
Mods.Description: Script Hook V is the library that allows to use GTA V script native functions in custom *.asi plugins. Note that it doesn't work in GTA Online, script hook closes GTA V when player goes in multiplayer, see details in the readme. This distrib also includes the latest Asi Loader and Native Trainer.

Mods.Name: ScriptHookVDotNet
Mods.Title: Script Hook V Dot Net
Mods.Description: Community Script Hook V .NET is an ASI plugin, which allows running scripts written in any .NET language ingame. It's full source code is hosted on Github (Changelog). Development is community-driven and open to everybody, so contributions are warmly welcomed.

Mods.Name: LemonUI
Mods.Title: Lemon UI
Mods.Description: LemonUI is a framework for creating UI systems in Grand Theft Auto V that is compatible with SHVDN2, SHVDN3 and FiveM. It allows you to create UI Elements with a NativeUI-like style, or you can also create your own UI System from scratch via the resolution-independant classes for Text, Rectangles and Textures.

Mods.Name: HKHModHelper
Mods.Title: HKH Mod Helper
Mods.Description: A mod Helper that quite a few of my mods use, mainly parts of mods that are used over and over, to make it more simple to edit combined these parts into one mod

Mods.Name: HKHBusinessHelper
Mods.Title: HKH Business Helper
Mods.Description: This simple mod will allow you to sell stocks, View current stocks count, sell the business, and order a vehicle from your garage, bunker, facility or Hanger!, all from a simple click of a button.

Mods.Name: EnableAllInteriors
Mods.Title: Enable All Interiors
Mods.Description:
Enable All Interiors or EAI, is a mod to enable All interiors in GTAV, this mod will be a full replacement for the following mods:
Open All Interiors
Online Interiors
Open Command Center Interiors (Still needed if your using Working Avenger, Working MOC, Working Terobyte, or their Business Mod Conterpart)
Open 60 Car Garage

Mods.Name: EnhancedTrains
Mods.Title: Enhanced Trains
Mods.Description: A simple script to make remove trains OR to make trains stop when somthing (vehicle/ped) is in front of them, might create more features later on.

Mods.Name: WhereAmIMinigame
Mods.Title: Where Am I Minigame
Mods.Description: A Minigame based on the internet game Geoguesser

Mods.Name: RecordMyRoute
Mods.Title: Record My Route
Mods.Description: Record My Route is a script that records your vehicles route and when you want you can press backspace to reset back to a saved position, to help if you fall of a mountain or bridge.

Mods.Name: EMPLauncherRework
Mods.Title: EMP Launcher Rework
Mods.Description: This mod aims to improves upon the EMP Launcher without the need for a mods folder.

Mods.Name: ActiveCamoScript
Mods.Title: Active Camo Script
Mods.Description: With this scirpt the player can turn invisible like the Doomsday Heist Juggernauts.

Mods.Name: San Andreas Weapon Pickups
Mods.Title: SanAndreasWeaponPickups
Mods.Description: This mod places around 80+ Weapon Pickups (as of the 1.0 update) around the map.

Mods.Name: BeaterDukesMinigame
Mods.Title: Beater Dukes Minigame
Mods.Description: Hidden Around Los Santos and Blaine County are 50 Wrecks of Beater Dukes, Collect all 50 to drive the restored car and earn 10m in cash.

Mods.Name: FlamethrowerScript
Mods.Title: Flamethrower Script
Mods.Description: This mod is a simple script to turn the Widowmaker from the Arena War Update into a flamethrower, the script will allow you to burn Peds, Vehicles, and even props

Mods.Name: RoamingBosses
Mods.Title: Roaming Bosses
Mods.Description: This mod adds Bossess, these Bossess have different abilities, like telporting, vanishing, explosive ammo, duplicating themselves.

Mods.Name: NavyRevolverHunt
Mods.Title: Navy Revolver Hunt
Mods.Description: This is a simple mod, to add in the Navy Revolver Mystery in Single Player

Mods.Name: AkulaStealthSystemsinSP
Mods.Title: Akula Stealth Systems in SP
Mods.Description: This mod allows the Akula to have a working stealth mode in SP, with a press of U the Cloak will charge a second later, your Akula will be almost undetectable

Mods.Name: Throwable Melee Weapons
Mods.Title: Throwable Melee Weapons
Mods.Description: This mod will allow you to throw melee Weapons!

Mods.Name: WorkingSkylift
Mods.Title: Working Skylift
Mods.Description: This simple mod, allows the user to use the skylifts magnet to pickup vehicles,at this stage you can only have 1 skylift carrying a vehicle

Mods.Name: MobileWardrobe
Mods.Title: Mobile Wardrobe
Mods.Description: This Mod simply adds a Mobile version of the Wardrobe, found in any of my Business mods, or Business Helper.

Mods.Name: MobileMoneyVault
Mods.Title: Mobile Money Vault
Mods.Description: This simple script allows the player to have a mobile version of the money vault (from my Arena War Business Latest version), you can have 10 slots to store money in, each one can hold around $2 Billion.

Mods.Name: TheCayoPericoHeistinSP
Mods.Title: The Cayo Perico Heist in SP
Mods.Description: The Cayo Perico Heist has finally arived to single player, ive taken the liberty to port the Cayo Perico Heist I made for my mod, 'The Payday Heist mod', to a standalone version.

Mods.Name: SlamtruckCarryMyVehicle
Mods.Title: Slamtruck Carry My Vehicle
Mods.Description: This simple script allows the Slamtruck from the Cayo Perico Heist to carry vehicles.

Mods.Name: IllegalGamblingDens
Mods.Title: Illegal Gambling Dens
Mods.Description: With this mod you will be able to play the casino games, specifically ones that ive recreated from GTAO, without the need for my DC&R Business, down by vespucci beach is a new location where you can go and gamble on any of the games in DC&R business.

Mods.Name: TheBusinessMegaPack
Mods.Title: The Business Mega Pack
Mods.Description: This is not a new mod it is just all business mods in one giant download as well as some extras that I recommend using to elevate your experience.

Mods.Name: PlayerCompanion
Mods.Title: Player Companion
Mods.Description: Player Companion is an expanded version of Hunk's Buddy Control, re-written from scratch, the mod allows you to have a bodyguard/friend/girlfriend in GTAV, hangout with your Companion to unlock new activities.

Mods.Name: WorkingBomber
Mods.Title: Working Bomber
Mods.Description: This simple mod allows you to use bombs in any aircaft that have got any of the 4 bomb types from smuggler's Run DLC.

Mods.Name: WorkingMOCinSP
Mods.Title: Working MOC in SP
Mods.Description: This allows any of the main three protagonists to use a fully functional Mobile Operations Center in Single Player!

Mods.Name: OpenCommandCenterInteriors
Mods.Title: Open Command Center Interiors
Mods.Description: What this mod does is kind of simple, it allows the Interiors of the MOC, Avenger and Terbyte to auto load when the player gets close.

Mods.Name: MK2WeaponGiver
Mods.Title: MK2 Weapon Giver
Mods.Description: This mod fixes the glitch that R* forgot to fix, concerning the MK2 weapons, where you reload the game and it resets the ammo count to 0.

Mods.Name: PersonalStripper
Mods.Title: Personal Stripper
Mods.Description: This mod allows you to call and have a stripper at any of the valid interiors.

Mods.Name: WorkingGalaxySuperYachtMod
Mods.Title: Working Galaxy Super Yacht Mod
Mods.Description: This mod allows you to use the Galaxy Super Yacht, in all 34 locations like in my Executive Business mod, the script was ported from Executive Business for a standalone version of the same script.

Mods.Name: SinglePlayerGarageReloaded
Mods.Title: Single Player Garage Reloaded
Mods.Description: So this mod does the same as SPG, allowing you to have unlimited garages, where ever you want.

Mods.Name: WorkingAvengerinSP
Mods.Title: Working Avenger in SP
Mods.Description: This mod makes the Avenger Function like it does online, note you cannot use just any old avenger, so head over to LSIA and pickup your personal avenger.

Mods.Name: PersonalHooker
Mods.Title: Personal Hooker
Mods.Description: This mod does what the mods name does, allows you to have a custom made hooker, avaiable in your phone contacts, the mod also supports the use of Addon Ped.

Mods.Name: WorkingJuggernautSuit
Mods.Title: Working Juggernaut Suit
Mods.Description: This simple mod allows any off the three protagonists to use the Juggernaut Suit from the Adversary mode, in GTA Online.

Mods.Name: WorkingTerrobyte
Mods.Title: Working Terrobyte
Mods.Description: This mod allows you to use the Terabyte Command Center, just like in GTAOnline, you can access the Oppressor MK2, and Oppressor, you can opperate a mobile drone for recon and much more.

Mods.Name: LestersBribes
Mods.Title: Lester's Bribes
Mods.Description: This mod adds the interaction menu from online where you can eat snacks, equip armour and the menu where u call Lester for options in online into one combined menu.

Mods.Name: ReplacePlayerVehicleScript
Mods.Title: Replace Player Vehicle Script
Mods.Description: This mod supports replacing Franklin's Buffalo and Bagger, Trevor's Bodhi and Quadbike, and Michael's Tailgater.

Mods.Name: SafehouseReloaded
Mods.Title: Safehouse Reloaded
Mods.Description: This mod is a perfect alternative to Single Player Apartment by I'm Not Mental, this mod adds in all Silthouse House, High End Appartments into Story Mode.

Mods.Name: AdvancedActions
Mods.Title: Advanced Actions
Mods.Description: This mod is a mod that allows the user to toggle custom Advanced Functions.

Mods.Name: WorkingKosotkaSubmarine
Mods.Title: Working Kosotka Submarine
Mods.Description: This mod turns the Kosotka Submarine, added in the Cayo Perico update into fully working.

Mods.Name: ThePaydayASinglePlayerHeistMod
Mods.Title: The Payday : A single Player Heist Mod
Mods.Description: The Payday is a Heist Mod, with Complete Heist, containing 3+ setups and 1 Finale, as of 4.0 there are 13 Heists Completed with another 3 heists coming.

Mods.Name: PersonalDriver
Mods.Title: Personal Driver
Mods.Description: Personal Driver is a simple mod that allows you to have a personal driver, that will drive you to a waypoint.

Mods.Name: WorkingFlatbed
Mods.Title: Working Flatbed
Mods.Description: This simple script allows you to use the flatbed truck as a vehicle carrier.

Mods.Name: WorkingWastelander
Mods.Title: Working Wastelander
Mods.Description: This simple mod allows you to use the Wastelander as a vehicle carrier.

Mods.Name: OnlineVehicleBlips
Mods.Title: Online Vehicle Blips
Mods.Description: This is a simple mod, that when you spawn a dlc vehicle, such as the Avenger, Akula, Barrage, APC, Halftrack, Molotok, Sterling the script will add its own blip like in gta online.

Mods.Name: LoadBunker/FacilityHatchesandInteriors
Mods.Title: Load Bunker/Facility Hatches and Interiors
Mods.Description: This mod is designed for my Gunrunning and Doomsday Heist mod.
